│   │
│   ├── core/
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   │
│   │   ├── activation.py       # ACT-R math (module ③ activation calculation)
│   │   │   ├── base_level_learning(timestamps, current_time, decay)
│   │   │   │   └── returns: float   # B(m) = ln(Σ t_k^(-d))
│   │   │   │
│   │   │   ├── spreading_activation(query_emb, topic_emb, context_chunks, weights)
│   │   │   │   └── returns: float   # SA = Σ W_j * cos_sim(query, topic)
│   │   │   │
│   │   │   ├── add_noise(sigma)
│   │   │   │   └── returns: float   # ε ~ Normal(0, σ)
│   │   │   │
│   │   │   └── total_activation(timestamps, query_emb, topic_emb, ...)
│   │   │       └── returns: ActivationResult  # A(m) = B + SA + ε
│   │   │
│   │   ├── topic_extractor.py  # topic extraction (module ② input processing)
│   │   │   ├── __init__(self)        # loads KeyBERT + spaCy models
│   │   │   ├── extract(message)      # pull topics/entities from a message
│   │   │   │   └── returns: list[Topic]
│   │   │   └── link_existing(new_topics, user_topics)
│   │   │       └── returns: list[TopicLink]  # cosine sim to existing topics
│   │   │
│   │   ├── context_builder.py  # context window assembly (module ② response gen)
│   │   │   ├── build(session_id, message, active_users, max_tokens)
│   │   │   │   └── returns: ContextWindow
│   │   │   ├── rank_topics(retrieved_topics, token_budget)
│   │   │   │   └── returns: list[Topic]  # fit best topics under token limit
│   │   │   └── format_context(topics, recent_messages)
│   │   │       └── returns: str          # formatted string for LLM prompt
│   │   │
│   │   └── production_rules.py # orchestration logic (module ② production rules)
│   │       ├── process_input(message, user_id, session_id)
│   │       │   └── decides: extract → store → retrieve → build → infer
│   │       ├── should_store(topic, confidence_threshold)
│   │       │   └── returns: bool
│   │       └── should_retrieve(message_type)
│   │           └── returns: bool  # skip retrieval for greetings etc.
